{"type": "article", "id": 31852, "title": "这个极简的壁钟，连钟面都省去了｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-09-05T23:31:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 20314, "name": "Färg & blanche"}, {"id": 32444, "name": "Revol"}, {"id": 32445, "name": "Poetic Lab"}, {"id": 32446, "name": "RAH:DESIGN"}, {"id": 32447, "name": "Bower"}, {"id": 32448, "name": "Studio Proba"}, {"id": 27093, "name": "Petite Friture"}, {"id": 32449, "name": "Jax & Bones"}, {"id": 32450, "name": "Modern House Numbers"}, {"id": 32451, "name": "Shel Han"}, {"id": 32452, "name": "Georg Åhrström"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 165, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160905233705d4u8UqtaTL12JxOR.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>SUCCESSION by FÄRG &amp; BLANCHE</h3><p>陶瓷和毛毡这两种完全不同的材料组合在一起会产生什么样的效果？最近，法国家居品牌 <a href=\"http://www.petitefriture.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Petite Friture</a> 与瑞典设计工作室 <a href=\"http://fargblanche.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">FÄRG &amp; BLANCHE</a>&nbsp;联手设计了一套名为 SUCCESSION 的餐具，在来自法国 <a href=\"http://www.revol1768.com/fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Revol</a> 瓷器工匠们的帮助下，通过浇铸技术在陶瓷表面留下毛毡特有的纹理。外部的哑光感和内部光滑的瓷釉带给人两种不同的视觉效果，显得非常别致。SUCCESSION 系列目前正在巴黎家居装饰博览会秋展上展出，这是它的<a href=\"http://www.petitefriture.com/fre/15/collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 14 到 55 欧元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905234118Hy2uPjdntDXvYbLT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905234118ZqobnmaLX9fVT46F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905234118pzCJ4kU9HNEQcZji.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744499\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905234118sl7Qh6SMCHx5UXWT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744499\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609052341189Kq8ECWbeHMtpfjU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.744499\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905234118qamMJ1RfjxXQeT7N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.765263\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>knock-down collection by Shel Han</h3><p>还记得我们之前介绍的一款无需螺丝就能完整组装的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/31647.html\">工作桌</a>吗？如果你喜欢这种轻轻松松就能 DIY 的家具设计，设计师 Shel Han 推出的 knock-down 系列能够让你像拼积木一样拼出十多种不同的家具。Han 的设计灵感来源于传统的中国细木工艺，所有的组件均由不刷漆的原木打造，自然极简的风格适用于各种不同的室内环境。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905234055YphGQZg8FNPrMoOy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905234057L1kwhTusl6BGveIt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905234057JxnBfLTybRwq9W5t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905234058pNUuvW7SJDLgFqjO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905234057tLHuiIs2vOw04XZd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905234057XSPARwyQo4lZm7MV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Silo Clock by Poetic Lab</h3><p>你见过需要自己排布钟面的壁钟吗？在巴黎家居装饰博览会秋展上，英国伦敦的 <a href=\"http://www.poetic-lab.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Poetic Lab</a> 工作室就带来了这款极简风格的 <a href=\"http://www.beyond-object.com/silo-clock\" rel=\"nofollow\">Silo Clock</a>。它本身并没有钟面，用户可以自由排布 12 个指标的位置，随意地进行改造。Silo 的时针和分针其实是两个不完整的三角形，随着时间的流逝它们所构成的形状也在不断地变化着，有一种能让人沉浸其中的美感。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.beyond-object.com/shop/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 100 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233757LXNtVA5xMv0FuJcl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.763959\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233759uEqn4gSDVNpiX3Cr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647208\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233801shDcdG9mL7ltw4fY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233801DeOJdw1pb2fPhW0s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.698393\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233805ithW93lIJdbPzBUC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.343063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233805uHaBkFrjtwg3oAZy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.093486\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>MDK9 Dog Haus by RAH:DESIGN</h3><p>谁说汪星人不能拥有设计感十足的房子？来自美国洛杉矶的家具订制公司 <a href=\"http://www.rahdesign-la.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">RAH:DESIGN</a> 利用巴西柚木、涂层金属以及混凝土打造了这款名为 MDK9 的狗屋。为了让它看上去更像是一个舒服的小房子，内部还配备了由 <a href=\"http://www.jaxandbones.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jax &amp; Bones</a> 提供的可定制的海绵枕，屋子正面则钉上了 <a href=\"http://www.modernhousenumbers.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Modern House Numbers</a> 制作的铝制宠物名牌，现代感十足。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.rahdesign-la.com/rahdog/mdk9-haus\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 3650 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233931fClN2d8DY3h9kTip.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685156\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233928HJ5nx7oMWi9CTXah.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233928ju9i3tdfyUPJ2GLw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.657813\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233928Xhqx5A0sKzbp2wgL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233928aysReMbtJul5KGdD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233931Flp5yf1RgwAjWQ7h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Atlas Lamp by Georg Åhrström</h3><p>为了让看起来枯燥乏味的大书架显得更生动活泼，瑞典设计师 <a href=\"http://www.ahrstromdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Georg Åhrström</a> 决定将灯具与书挡的功能结合在一起，设计了这款会发光的书挡 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/41544321/Atlas-Lamp\" rel=\"nofollow\">Atlas Lamp</a>。尽管它不像是其他卡通造型的书挡（比如我们之前介绍的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/25718.html\">女超人款</a>）那样有着吸睛的独特外观，但它可以通过一道道像是书脊一样的光线帮你将不同的书籍区分开来，简单而实用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233841JvVt9idKlTEYrsMS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233840HVeWhDU8x1COryiG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609052338420DOHKd3VjPfYZIxX.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609052338399X8plI5AKEZdcbi4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233838rWVnKSmMj7zCxG3F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233839t8p5yBW0aUc4uigR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Waterline Chair by Bower &amp; Studio Proba</h3><p>这张将脆弱和坚韧两种特质融合在一起的座椅名为 <a href=\"http://bowernyc.com/waterline-chair\" rel=\"nofollow\">Waterline Chair</a>，由纽约设计工作室 <a href=\"http://bowernyc.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bower</a> 和 <a href=\"http://www.studioproba.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studio Proba</a> 共同打造。它有一个染成桃红色的玻璃底座，玻璃的边缘特意做成了水线般起伏的造型，上面放置了四块天鹅绒软垫：红色座位和玻璃底座的搭配看上去非常协调，三块灰色的软垫组成了座椅的扶手和靠背，给人一种端正而优雅的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233903UwBaFpb8RSmNW0Ec.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.630000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233904gm9uONJZ7vldPe3f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233903poTNXn03YFS7hCa8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.711667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233904PoqCBXQxYE1irpF9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233904e461a0EYNBzXWqTc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160905233903Gbfq5Ra8ndSetQv6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}